<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title><%= config.title %></title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 20px;
    }
    a:link, a:visited {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: rgb(96, 143, 219);
    }
    a:hover, a:active {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= config.title %></h1>
    <h2>Available Endpoints</h2>
    <p>
      This service provides a subset of JSKOS API (as implemented in <a href="https://github.com/gbv/jskos-server" target="_blank">in JSKOS-Server</a>) to access Wikibase instance <a href="<%= config.wikibase.instance %>"><%= config.wikibase.instance %></a> in
      <a href="https://gbv.github.io/jskos/jskos.html">JSKOS format</a>.
      See <a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos/">https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos/</a> for source code and issue tracker.
    </p>
    <h3>General</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        GET <a href="status">/status</a> - Returns a status object
        (<a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos#get-status" target="_blank">documentation</a>)
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Concepts</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        GET <a href="concepts">/concepts</a> - Returns detailed data for concepts
        (<a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos#get-concepts" target="_blank">documentation</a>)
        <br><em>example:</em>
        <a href="concept?uri=http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q42">concept?uri=http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q42</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        GET <a href="concepts">/concepts/suggest</a> - Returns concept suggestions
        (<a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos#get-concepts-suggest" target="_blank">documentation</a>)
        <br>
        <em>example:</em>
        <a href="concepts/suggest?search=G%C3%B6ttingen&language=de">concepts/suggest?search=GÃ¶ttingen&amp;language=de</a>
      </li>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Mappings</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        GET <a href="mappings">/mappings</a> - Returns a list of mappings
        (<a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos#get-mappings" target="_blank">documentation</a>)
        <br><em>examples:</em>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="mappings?from=http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2013">mappings?from=http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2013</a></li>
      <li><a href="mappings?to=http://d-nb.info/gnd/7527800-5">mappings?to=http://d-nb.info/gnd/7527800-5</a></li>
      <li><a href="mappings/?direction=both&mode=or&from=http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q42395&to=http://d-nb.info/gnd/4074195-3">mappings?direction=both&amp;mode=and&amp;from=http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q42395&amp;to=http://d-nb.info/gnd/4074195-3</a></li>
      <li><a href="mappings/?direction=both&mode=or&from=http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q42395&to=http://d-nb.info/gnd/4074195-3">mappings?direction=both&amp;mode=or&amp;from=http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q42395&amp;to=http://d-nb.info/gnd/4074195-3</a></li>
      <li><a href="mappings?toScheme=http://bartoc.org/en/node/18785">mappings?toScheme=http://bartoc.org/en/node/18785</a></li>
    </ul>

      </li>
      <li>
        POST /mappings - Saves a mapping in Wikidata (authentication needed)
        (<a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos-#post-mappings" target="_blank">documentation</a>)
      </li>
      <li>
        PUT /mappings/:_id - Overwrites a mapping in Wikidata (authentication needed)
        <a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos#put-mappings_id" target="_blank">documentation</a>)
      </li>
      <li>
        DELETE /mappings/:_id - Deletes a mapping in Wikidata (authentication needed)
        <a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos#delete-mappings_id" target="_blank">documentation</a>)
      </li>
      <li>
        GET <a href="mappings/voc">/mappings/voc</a> - Returns a list of concept schemes used in mappings
        (<a href="https://github.com/gbv/wikidata-jskos#get-mappingsvoc" target="_blank">documentation</a>)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html>
